    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="original">
                <pb facs="EHRI-ET-WL05320006_01.jpg" n="1"/>
                <p>קאָמיטעט צו זאַמלען מאַטעריאַלן</p>
                <p>וועגן ייִדישן חורבן אין <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_poles" type="subject">פּוילן</term> 1939</p>
                <p>
                    <persName ref="#ehri_et_blumberg_leyb" type="ehri">בלומבערג לייב</persName>
                </p>
                <p>געבוירן 1915, <placeName ref="#warsaw" type="ehri">וואַרשע</placeName>
                </p>
                <p>פּראָטאָקאָל נומער 6</p>
                <p>(צוזאַמענגעשטעלט דעם 16טן נאָוועמבער 1939)</p>
                <p>אַרויס פֿון <placeName ref="#warsaw" type="ehri">וואַרשע</placeName> דעם 14טן אָקטאָבער. געווען די גאַנצע צײַט <term ref="#t262"
                        type="subject">אויסבאַהאַלטן</term> אויף <placeName ref="#warsaw" type="ehri">באָניפֿראַטערסקאַ 4</placeName>. אַליין ניט
                    בײַגעווען קיינע שום סצענעס. דאָס הויז – ניט געליטן פֿון די <term ref="#t1083" type="subject">באָמבאַרדירונגען</term>.</p>
                <p>קיין <placeName ref="#vilnius" type="ehri">ווילנע</placeName> אַריבער מיטן וועג <placeName ref="#malkinia-gorna" type="ehri"
                        >מאַלקין</placeName> ־ <placeName ref="#bialystok" type="ehri">ביאַליסטאָק</placeName>. געגאַנגען צוזאַמען מיט אַ קאָמפּאַניע
                        <term ref="#t763" type="subject">קריסטלעכע</term> אַרבעטער, וועלכע זײַנען געגאַנגען צו די <term
                        ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_soviets" type="subject">סאָוויעטן</term>, געווען דאָ אויך אַ <term ref="#t650" type="subject"
                        >געפֿאַנגענער</term> פֿון <placeName ref="#vilnius" type="ehri">ווילנער</placeName> געגנט. אַזוי אַרום איז דער וועג אַריבער
                    בשלום, די <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans" type="subject">דײַטשן</term> נישט געטשעפּעט.</p>
                <p>געהערט אַ סך דערציילונגען, אָבער געדענקט זיי ניט.</p>
                <p>די גרענעץ געווען אָפֿן, אַריבער אָן שום שוועריקייטן קיין <placeName ref="#vilnius" type="ehri">ווילנע</placeName>.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="transcription">
                <pb facs="EHRI-ET-WL05320006_01.jpg" n="1"/>
                <p><note type="gloss">stamp on the left:</note> Committee to Collect Material</p>
                <p>about the Destruction of <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_poles">Polish</term> Jewry <date when="1939">1939</date></p>
                <p><persName ref="#ehri_et_blumberg_leyb" type="ehri">Blumberg Leyb</persName></p>
                <p>Born in <date when="1915">1915</date>, <placeName ref="#warsaw" type="ehri">Warsaw</placeName></p>
                <p>Testimony number 6</p>
                <p>(recorded on <date when="1939-11-16">16th November, 1939</date>)</p>
                <p>I <note type="gloss">There are no personal pronouns and no auxiliary verbs in the record (probably in order to save time), so it’s
                        impossible to know if it is the 1st or the 3rd person.</note> left <placeName ref="#warsaw" type="ehri">Warsaw</placeName> on
                        <date when="1939-10-14">14th October</date>. Before, I had been <term ref="#t262" type="subject">hidden</term> all the time on
                        <placeName ref="#warsaw" type="ehri">Bonifraterska street 4</placeName>. I didn’t see any scenes. The house was not damaged by
                        <term ref="#t1083" type="subject">bombings</term>.</p>
                <p>I reached <placeName ref="#vilnius" type="ehri">Vilnius</placeName> by the <placeName ref="#malkinia-gorna" type="ehri"
                        >Małkinia</placeName> – <placeName ref="#bialystok" type="ehri">Białystok</placeName> road. I went on foot, in the company of
                        <term ref="#t763" type="subject">Christian</term> workers who were going to the <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_soviets"
                        type="subject">Soviets</term>. There was also a <term ref="#t650" type="subject">prisoner</term> from the region of <placeName
                        ref="#vilnius" type="ehri">Vilnius</placeName>. We got through safely, the <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans"
                        >Germans</term> did not bother us.</p>
                <p>I heard a lot of stories, but don’t remember any.</p>
                <p>The border was open, we reached <placeName ref="#vilnius" type="ehri">Vilnius</placeName> without difficulties.</p>
            </div>
